  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The effects of hydrocortisone on cognition will be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      80 healthy young individuals (40 females and 40 male) will be recruited an randomized to
      either placebo or 10 mg hydrocortisone before testing. Tasks will on emotion recognition,
      memory and cognitive flexibilty will be conducted.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
